msgid "Cheap and fast transport. Ideal for early raids and first logistics routes."
msgstr "Transport rapide et economique. Ideal pour les premiers raids et routes logistiques."

msgid "Moves large resource loads, but slows the fleet and needs an escort."
msgstr "Deplace de grandes charges de ressources, mais ralentit la flotte et demande une escorte."

msgid "Fast and cheap attack craft. Excellent for hunting freighters and exposed bombers."
msgstr "Vaisseau d attaque rapide et economique. Excellent pour chasser cargos et bombardiers exposes."

msgid "First stable military ship. Protects freighters and gives early fleets consistency."
msgstr "Premier vaisseau militaire stable. Protege les cargos et stabilise les premieres flottes."

msgid "Opening burst damage ship. Strong against shields and light defenses, weak in long battles."
msgstr "Vaisseau de degats initiaux. Fort contre boucliers et defenses legeres, faible en combat long."

msgid "Fast ship for serious raids. Carries its own cargo and hits vulnerable targets hard."
msgstr "Vaisseau rapide pour raids serieux. Transporte sa cargaison et frappe fort les cibles vulnerables."

msgid "Mid-game military core. Useful for attack, defense and escort duties."
msgstr "Coeur militaire de milieu de partie. Utile en attaque, defense et escorte."

msgid "Direct counter to fighter swarms, corvettes and raiding fleets."
msgstr "Contre direct aux essaims de chasseurs, corvettes et flottes de raid."

msgid "Specialized ship for destroying defenses. It needs an escort."
msgstr "Vaisseau specialise dans la destruction des defenses. Il a besoin d une escorte."

msgid "Designed for planetary blockade missions. It wins through strategic control, not raw damage."
msgstr "Concu pour les missions de blocus planetaire. Il gagne par controle strategique, pas par degats bruts."

msgid "Enables new colonies. Strategic, expensive and worth protecting."
msgstr "Permet de fonder de nouvelles colonies. Strategique, couteux et a proteger."

msgid "Reliable heavy ship. Protects bombers, blockers and strategic craft."
msgstr "Vaisseau lourd fiable. Protege bombardiers, bloqueurs et vaisseaux strategiques."

